{"tid":1761832,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇香港電腦學會member？想入會","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T15:06:01.000Z","uid":255359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"600a0ef70b3db83ee6ab8ee2fef1d1d61b8df720","tid":1761832,"uid":255359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人知個membership有冇用？要8舊水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我主要想入功能界別投票<br />\n但係需要full member，而fullmember好似要兩個推薦人<br />\n有冇人介紹下我入會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他入會要求我都達標，幫手推推，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a8d11919d2b018bba0275a57acc9b87abf4847","tid":1761832,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"P for pushing"},{"pid":"43aaa62ed43aad70bf30bdf106d03ea57dc8b421","tid":1761832,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55601b85f21676f87c6765460d8ceffd56c0e9d5","tid":1761832,"uid":255359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"710fd9a81d8cc5ff579e7dd216804c1e3bc89573","tid":1761832,"uid":81353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98961e2220e04903b1bac7adef4781905a5aa68c","tid":1761832,"uid":62116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a7c7c64b009ab8a1b04387f230162f5bf9aa60e","tid":1761832,"uid":88676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a2b26cc73963ae2d913c18c3dfb3680b45dd0b8","tid":1761832,"uid":238948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6cfb2ed799f67c5a19b70fa4a1ba9976facb58ea","tid":1761832,"uid":177215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"51616c9c276b4c73f1fb93320b6a5ed09fd68ffb","tid":1761832,"uid":255359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"［時代革命，寸土必爭，下一個戰場 &gt; 功、能、組、別！］<br />\n<br />\n區選大勝後，北京可控制特首選委票，已經由777票急降至660票，所以我地下一步要劍指功能組別，再𠝹走佢60票！咁樣下次邊個做特首，將會由香港人主導！<br />\n<br />\n再者，假若控制立法會工能組別及直選議席，我地便可以運用權力及特權法，獨立調查警暴！！唔洗求人！<br />\n<br />\n其實身邊好多朋友本身已經成為專業人仕，如果你符合以下資格，我跪求你盡快登記！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=bd98bcc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n <br />\n* 資訊科技界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：12000人<br />\n資格： 香港電腦學會會員（交800蚊會費同埋有電腦學位和4年經驗就得！）<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/it_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fit_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=3cfb734f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/it_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 工程界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：9400人<br />\n資格： 註冊的專業工程師<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/eng_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Feng_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a1e86f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/eng_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 教育界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：80000人<br />\n資格： 註冊教師<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/edu_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fedu_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=7fc58bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/edu_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 會計界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：26000人<br />\n資格： 註冊的會計師 （外國CPA快d睇下點可accredit 去攞埋HKICPA!)<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/acc_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Facc_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=cc2428aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/acc_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 醫學界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：11000人<br />\n資格： 註冊醫生, 註冊牙醫<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/med_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fmed_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=c8ad8398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/med_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 法律界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：6700人<br />\n資格： 香港律師,大律師<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/leg_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fleg_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=b60384cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/leg_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 社會福利界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：60人<br />\n已登記選民：14000人<br />\n資格： 註冊社工<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/sw_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fsw_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=8f5d2458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/sw_c.pdf</a><br />\n <br />\n* 建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界 *<br />\n特首選委人數：30人<br />\n已登記選民：7300人<br />\n資格： 註冊的建築師, 園境師, 專業測量師, 專業規劃師<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/aspl_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Faspl_c.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=db0c9aca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/aspl_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n 仲有其他界別不能盡錄，詳見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FCSS.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2FFCSS.htm&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a6b87d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FCSS.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 快快行動 + 轉 + 呼籲你認識同事/朋友們登記！<br />\n<br />\n 抗爭六個月了，香港的小朋友們已經超額付出佢地所有前途甚至寶貴生命，佢地嘅血和淚將呢場香港民主運動推至前所未有的高度和亮度。所以係時候由我地呢班和理非做番少少野。如果北京見到功能組別選民人數急昇，佢地就會知道大勢已去，速速回應五大訴求（正所謂攞番個尾彩），免得到頭來比香港人自己響體制內翻盤，自討沒趣！"},{"pid":"34b33c5a280d903d68f4f4b402f8e889f61b6a1b","tid":1761832,"uid":255359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"剛才爬文搵到<br />\n希望幫到大家，原來唔駛member referral<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tC1sizr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC1sizr.jpg&h=e87ccb66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113bf802235566b5b40e0bd04d662af40e321666","tid":1761832,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWemmrP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWemmrP.jpg&h=50a0c385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>運動未完 仍需努力</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4e8dd78125ef93c491d85d6363566c821cee5d20","tid":1761832,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"HK is not California<br />\n<br />\nHKNOIT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5819ee3e45e30ccca3c15b1a92908cc93c6e453","tid":1761832,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4176ea1f26fa62e5744b3a7b2ba7fa7479847c12","tid":1761832,"uid":19621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"ieee好似都得"},{"pid":"a71a4b9e5970ced27d5269ab3a8ea71b45b1d61c","tid":1761832,"uid":55367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"早排有人share.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fltw.github.io/ITVOTER.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.